NG0201:1: ta ki dza de byi dzahde hum ya hum ya /
NG0201:2: hu lu hu lu pu ru te pu ru swa ha /
NG0201:3: zhes brjod nas che ba rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs so //
NG0201:4: de nas rigs bzhi'i klu rnams la //
NG0201:5: rab tu che ba bstan pa'i phyir //
NG0201:6: nyid kyi gzhal yas khang chen po //
NG0201:7: rab tu brjid pa 'di nyid du //
NG0201:8: byol song rigs bzhi dang thabs cig tu 'dug pa'i gnas 'di lta ste //
NG0201:9: rgya mtsho chen po'i dbus gnas 'bar //
NG0201:10: ri rab mchod rten gzugs 'dra la //
NG0201:11: bum pa yid bzhin lcang los brgyan //
NG0201:12: sbrul gnyis dar 'phyang lta bus mdzes //
NG0201:13: rigs bzhi'i rgyan gyis rab tu bklubs //
NG0201:14: sgo bzhi ka brgyad rab tu ldan //
NG0201:15: de 'og gsum gnyis rab tu mdzes //
NG0201:16: byol song longs spyod rab tu ldan //
NG0201:17: de nyid bum pa'i khong seng na //
NG0201:18: gser mig 'bar ba dang thabs cig tu bzhugs pa 'di lta ste /
NG0201:19: gzi brjid mtha' yas dung skyong dang *//
NG0201:20: gang po nor ldan la sogs dang *//
NG0201:21: dga' bo 'jog po ma dros dang *//
NG0201:22: rigs bzhi'i gtso bo klu brgyad de //
NG0201:23: sku la 'khril te rab tu gnas //
NG0201:24: gyad nor med la sogs pa'i rgyan //
NG0201:25: dar dpyang ma dang pad+ma'i rgyan //
NG0201:26: gzi brjid ma dang dung can ma //
NG0201:27: klu mo rigs bzhi la sogs pa dang thabs cig tu bzhugs so //
NG0201:28: de nas bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed pos gnyen po sgrub pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0201:29: dgon pa dur khrod mtsho gling ngam //
NG0201:30: chu mig nags na gnas pa'i bar //
NG0201:32: dri spos sman gyis chag chag gdab //
NG0201:33: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud ldan //
NG0201:34: sgo bzhi rigs dang ldan pa bri //
NG0201:35: dbus su lag na rdo rje ste //
NG0201:36: 'khor lo bzhi la bya khyung bzhi //
NG0201:37: gru chad mchod pa'i bum pa bzhi //
NG0201:38: sman lnga spos lnga rin chen lnga //
NG0201:39: 'bru lnga me tog lnga la sogs //
NG0201:40: bcu gnyis lnga nyid byin gyis brlab //
NG0201:41: sgo la mchod pa'i gtor ma bzhi //
NG0201:42: b+ha ma hasti bcas pa yi //
NG0201:43: sor mo lnga yi bcangs pa'i rjes //
NG0201:44: mkha' lding mchod pa'i rdzas su gzhag / de nas ting 'dzin rim pa ni //
NG0201:45: dang po stong pa'i byang chub sems //
NG0201:46: gnyis pa snying rje 'byung ba dang *//
NG0201:47: gsum pa rgyu yi rnam pa las //
NG0201:48: bam gyi sa bon las byung ba'i //
NG0201:49: rgya mtsho chen po'i dbus su ni //
NG0201:50: lam las ri rab rin chen bskyed //
NG0201:51: de steng khrom las ga ru da /
NG0201:52: rdo rje gshog pa'i byin rlabs las //
NG0201:53: bya khyung rgyal po bzhi byung bas //
NG0201:54: dkar dang dmar dang ser dang ljang *//
NG0201:55: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i steng du bsgom //
NG0201:56: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du //
NG0201:57: ye shes mkha' lding stobs po che //
NG0201:59: dbu gsum rdo rje'i mchu khra la //
NG0201:60: ring la dmar zhing spyan yang dmar //
NG0201:61: zhal gdangs ral pa sprugs pa'i tshul //
NG0201:62: ye shes gshog gdengs sku yang shin tu g.yo //
NG0201:63: sku dang yan lag rin chen baidur brgyan //
NG0201:64: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po 'khor @#//
NG0201:66: bar pa lcags kyu tha ma thal mo sbyar //
NG0201:67: g.yon gyi dang pos rin chen zur brgyad bsnams //
NG0201:68: bar pa zhags pa tha ma thal mo sbyar //
NG0201:69: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su //
NG0201:70: ye shes mkha' lding rgyal po gzi brjid 'od po che //
NG0201:71: dbu gsum mdog dmar ral pa lcang lor 'khyil //
NG0201:72: zhal gdangs ye shes gshog pa chen po gdengs //
NG0201:73: sku dang ye shes yan lag me chen 'bar //
NG0201:74: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NG0201:75: bar ma lcags kyu tha ma rin po che //
NG0201:76: g.yon gyi dang po rdo rje pad+ma 'phyar //
NG0201:77: bar ma zhags pa tha ma dbyug to bsnams //
NG0201:78: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su //
NG0201:79: ye shes mkha' lding rgyal po mi mgo can //
NG0201:80: dbu gsum mdog ser ral pa gyen du 'khyil //
NG0201:81: yan lag rin chen sku las me chen 'bar //
NG0201:82: ye shes gshog pa rgya chen brkyang bskum mdzad //
NG0201:83: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po rin chen 'bar //
NG0201:84: bar ma lcags kyu tha ma dpag bsam shing *//
NG0201:85: g.yon gyi dang po ye shes ral gri 'phyar //
NG0201:86: bar ma zhags pa tha ma gshog tshul brkyang *//
NG0201:87: byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du //
NG0201:88: ye shes mkha' lding rlung gi shugs //
NG0201:89: dbu gsum mdog ljang ral pa 'khyil //
NG0201:90: sgra skad sna tshogs bzhad cing smin ma bskyod //
NG0201:91: yan lag rin chen brgyan pas sku 'bar ba //
NG0201:92: phyag drug g.yas kyi dang po ral gri phyar //
NG0201:93: bar ma lcags kyu tha ma shing thog bi ja pur //
NG0201:94: g.yon gyi dang po 'khor lo 'bar ba bsnams //
NG0201:95: bar ma zhags pa tha ma gshog tshul brkyang *//
NG0201:96: de rnams rtsa ba'i snying po khrom las bskyed //
NG0201:97: de bzhin spyan drang bzhugs gsol phyag bya dang *//
NG0201:98: mchod dang bstod dang bzlas pa tshul bzhin bya //
NG0201:99: ba lim la sogs byed pa dang *//
NG0201:100: b+ha ma hasti bcings pa yis //
NG0201:101: sor mo lnga yis bcangs pa'i rjes //
NG0201:102: zan chang dkar gsum 'bru dang sman gyis mchod //
NG0201:103: om ra dza ma ha ga ru da /
NG0201:104: hum ba lim pu tsa ba lim ta kha hi /
NG0201:106: de nas sngags 'di rgyun du bzlas //
NG0201:107: ong kam ong kam khyung ka ra khyung ka ra /
NG0201:109: om badzra ma ha kro d+ha hum phat /
NG0201:110: sngags de rtsa ba rgyun du drangs //
NG0201:111: mkha' lding gso ba'i las byed na //
NG0201:112: bdag gam gzhan la gdug pas 'jigs //
NG0201:113: ga ru rgyal po mchod 'dod pas //
NG0201:114: gnas sam khang pa'i sgo ngos te //
NG0201:115: snum pa'i sa'am bag zan la //
NG0201:116: ga ru da yi gzugs bcas te //
NG0201:117: ba lim la sogs pu tsa dang *//
NG0201:118: b+ha ma hasti bcings pa yi //
NG0201:119: sor mo lnga yi pu tsa des //
NG0201:120: ga ru da nyid la ni dbul //
NG0201:121: snying po lnga po gang yang rung *//
NG0201:122: gcig gis sna drangs brjod rt-ing la //
NG0201:123: ga ru da gnyis brjod nas kyang *//
NG0201:124: de rting pu dza rab tu brjod //
NG0201:125: thog mar om dang swa has dbul /
NG0201:126: 'di ltar gzhung bzhin byas nas ni //
NG0201:127: ka la sha tas zin pa la //
NG0201:128: grol bar 'gyur ba the tshom med //
NG0201:129: de nas gnyen po rigs bzhi la //
NG0201:133: rig sngags bdag po mthu stobs bdag po'i sku //
NG0201:134: e ma'o phyag gi mthil na rdo rje 'bar 'dra bas //
NG0201:135: zhal nas gsungs skad bton pas khams gsum dbang du sdud //
NG0201:136: stong gsum drag tu g.yos pas klu chen pho mo 'dul //
NG0201:137: mkha' lding rgyal po 'jigs byed ga ru da /
NG0201:138: lcags kyu 'dab gshog chen po brgyang bas ni /
NG0201:139: gser gyi 'od 'phro rlung sgra drag po yis //
NG0201:140: rgya mtsho chen por kun tu brdabs pa yis //
NG0201:141: klu rgyal 'khor dang bcas pa zil gyis gnon //
NG0201:142: 'jigs byed gser gyi spyan rnon chen pos ni //
NG0201:143: tshangs pa chen po'i yul sa rtse nas gnon //
NG0201:144: gal te klu rnams dam las 'das gyur na //
NG0201:145: rgya mtsho'i snying po rgya mtsho'i lbu ba la //
NG0201:146: gshog pa chen po rgya mtshor byas nas ni //
NG0201:147: klu rnams thams cad dbang du bsdus nas ni //
NG0201:148: me yi snying po 'bar bas bsreg byas te //
NG0201:149: lus ni rul myags dri ni nga bar 'gyur //
NG0201:150: nad kyi rnam grangs mang pos 'debs pa dang *//
NG0201:151: lus la nad ngan sha bkra 'byung bar 'gyur //
NG0201:152: ga ru da tsa le tsa le hum phat /
NG0201:153: hum nam mkha' lding gi rgyal po tshangs pa'i bya //
NG0201:154: gser 'dab bya khyung ga ru da //
NG0201:155: drang srong 'khor gyi stobs po che //
NG0201:156: rigs gsum mgon po rdo rje rgyal //
NG0201:157: mnga' ris 'khor du klu yis bskor //
NG0201:158: rdo rje rnon po spu gri'i so gnyis gtsigs //
NG0201:159: gser gyi spyan gnyis khro gnyer can //
NG0201:160: thabs ldan rdo rje'i rwa gnyis brjid //
NG0201:161: yid bzhin nor bu gtsug na 'bar //
NG0201:162: lcags kyi mchu chen rno dbal gyis //
NG0201:163: rab tu gdug pa'i klu rnams spyi nas 'dren //
NG0201:164: rdo rje'i sder gshog brkyangs pa'i rlung mo ches //
NG0201:165: klu rgyal gdug pa dbang du sdud par mdzad //
NG0201:166: ces bstod de dbang du bsdu'o //
NG0201:167: dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:168: gdug pa glu bsgrub kyi zla gsang gi skabs te
NG0201:169: nga lnga pa'o // // de nas yang bcom ldan
NG0201:170: 'das gshin rje gshed pos gdug pa klu bsgrub 'di
NG0201:171: yang gsungs / mtsho 'gram chu mig shing gcig rkang *//
NG0201:172: nags rdzongs mthug po dur khrod du //
NG0201:174: ba las byung ba'i rnam pa lnga //
NG0201:175: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga la byug / de nyid byin gyis brlab pa'i phyir //
NG0201:176: hum sa ma ya om gyi sngags //
NG0201:177: bya ba byed pas byin gyis brlab //
NG0201:178: bdag nyid chen por rab brtags te //
NG0201:179: thams cad grub par bya ba'i phyir //
NG0201:180: bdag nyid spyi bor sa dmigs te //
NG0201:181: bdag po bzhi yis dbang bskur ro //
NG0201:182: rdo rje'i sbu gur ma bsams te //
NG0201:183: g.yu bye'u sngon mos dbang bskur ro //
NG0201:184: tri dang ya bsam dregs pas dbang bskur bya'o //
NG0201:185: snying gar hum bskyed bdag dbang bskur //
NG0201:186: lte bar om yig gnyen por ro //
NG0201:187: de nas thig dang ri mo bri //
NG0201:189: gru chad sgo rnams de bzhin bri //
NG0201:190: lte ba mthing ga pad+ma dkar //
NG0201:191: mu khyud dmar po gru chad @#//
NG0201:193: sgo rnams ser po sgo 'bur rigs //
NG0201:194: de bzhin tshon rnams dgye bar bya //
NG0201:195: dbus su gnyen po dgod par bya //
NG0201:196: pad+ma brgyad la klu chen brgyad //
NG0201:197: rang rang rtsa ba'i sngags kyang bri //
NG0201:198: rtsibs mchan de mi bri bar bya //
NG0201:199: gru chad bzhi la klu mo bzhi //
NG0201:200: na ba phu na gru chad la //
NG0201:201: sgo 'bur ha sa tram ga rnams //
NG0201:202: shar nas bskor te rim par dgod //
NG0201:203: ces rgyun du bzlas pa'i yi ge dgu po 'di gsungs so //
NG0201:204: hum na ga ra dza sa ma ya che ge mo zhig tsit+ta dz+wa la zhes bsgrub par bya'o //
NG0201:205: zhag dgu bar du khrus byas te //
NG0201:206: zas rnams lnga ni spang bar bya //
NG0201:207: de nas grub pa'i rtags rnams ni //
NG0201:208: dngos su longs spyod tshogs rnams 'byung *//
NG0201:209: bar ni bas ldag thor ba 'byung *//
NG0201:210: de nyid mngon du gyur tshe'o //
NG0201:211: rig pa'i sham du gdags par bya //
NG0201:212: smi ti gi ti las la gzud //
NG0201:213: ces don thams cad grub par bya ba'i phyir //
NG0201:214: dbang bskur bar bya ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0201:215: dar dkar gzhi ma btings nas ni //
NG0201:217: dkar po la sogs mu khyud ldan //
NG0201:218: dbus su dam tshig sa bon sa na 'dra min 'dug sa ha dgod //
NG0201:219: de nas yid 'ong bum pa la //
NG0201:220: bdun pa dgu pa'i ri mo bri //
NG0201:221: dge bsnyen gnyis por rab tu dmigs //
NG0201:222: kha dog tshang ba'i ras kyis bcings //
NG0201:223: rma bya 'om bu bra ma dang *//
NG0201:224: drag po'i rdzas la bdug par bya //
NG0201:225: ras la sogs pa'i gzungs thag gdags //
NG0201:226: sder gshog phyag rgya snying gar bstan //
NG0201:227: sman lnga spos lnga rin chen lnga //
NG0201:228: 'bru lnga me tog lnga la sogs //
NG0201:229: bcu gnyis lnga nyid byin gyis brlab //
NG0201:230: a+om ahhum na ga yu lu /
NG0201:231: na ga yu ru dz+wa la ni /
NG0201:232: na ga sa ma ya swa ha /
NG0201:233: dmigs pa'i yan lag gsum pa'i rgyud //
NG0201:234: yi ge rtsa gcig sbrul par bshad //
NG0201:235: hum skyes bdag po gnyis nas sprul //
NG0201:236: yan lag yi ge rtsa gcig las //
NG0201:237: 'od zer sna tshogs bdud rtsir sprul //
NG0201:238: yi ge dmigs pa'i gnas lnga ru //
NG0201:239: bdud rtsi bum pa brtan par bya //
NG0201:240: mkha' lding rgyal po de nyid bsam //
NG0201:241: de nyid gtsang ma'i ras kyis dkris //
NG0201:242: gur gum sman nam chus bsres bkru //
NG0201:243: de bzhin ma smin zas rnams bza' //
NG0201:245: kye ma'o rdo rje 'dzin pa'i bdag / bdag gi dam tshig mngon dga' bas //
NG0201:247: khyod kyi dam tshig gtso lags kyi //
NG0201:248: longs spyod klu yi pho brang nas //
NG0201:249: rigs pa'i rgyal pos dbang bskur cig / ces gsol to //
NG0201:250: nyon cig skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NG0201:251: longs spyod klu yi rigs kyis 'grub //
NG0201:252: pho brang yid 'ong mngon dga' nas //
NG0201:253: rab tu gdug pa'i klu rnams la //
NG0201:254: yid bzhin rin chen rab gnas pas //
NG0201:255: de ring khyod kyis bcang bar gyis //
NG0201:257: de nas yang bar chad bsal ba'i phyir //
NG0201:258: rma byas brdeg cing gu gul bdug / ces gsungs so //
NG0201:259: snying po rigs bzhi dbu rgyan @#//
NG0201:261: dar gyi cod pan me tog phreng *//
NG0201:262: longs spyod tshogs gyi zhal zas dang *//
NG0201:263: rten gyi bum pas dbang bskur bya'o //
NG0201:264: de nas dam tshig rten 'brel gyi snying po 'di sbyin par bya'o //
NG0201:265: rigs ldan thogs med rgyug pa yi //
NG0201:266: sngags ldan sngags kyi bdag po khyod //
NG0201:267: de ring dam tshig 'di zung la //
NG0201:268: yid bzhin rin chen gter bzhin chongs //
NG0201:269: nam mkha'i dngos po mi gnas la //
NG0201:271: snang med sprul ba'i ngo bo las //
NG0201:272: rnam shes ldan pa'i thogs med ni //
NG0201:273: rnam shes sku yi ngo bo las //
NG0201:274: yi ge phreng ba nyid du bkod //
NG0201:275: na ga li li hri la pa tri sni ra /
NG0201:277: tri ya ku ru pa tri yam /
NG0201:278: he he hum hum b+h+yo dza /
NG0201:279: zhes rten 'brel gyi snying pos yongs su rdzogs par bya'o //
NG0201:280: de bsgrub bar du klu las gad mi bya //
NG0201:281: de yi sbyor ba yongs su rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0201:282: klu yi sbyor ba tshang bar bsag par bya //
NG0201:283: 'di ni dang por sngon du rab tu gces //
NG0201:284: de nas klu yi sbyor ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0201:285: na ga gnas shing gar na gnas pa'i sa //
NG0201:286: de yi drung nas 'jam pa'i sa blangs la //
NG0201:287: sa gnyen sbyin po dag dang mnyam bsres la //
NG0201:288: klu yi ra dza de yi gzugs byas la //
NG0201:289: lus bcu mgo gcig sbrul mgo bdun gyis brgyan //
NG0201:290: g.yas na rin chen 'bar ba'i bum pa thogs //
NG0201:291: kha dog mthing ga lus kyis chu srin mnan //
NG0201:292: pho yi yi ge 'di ni 'di yi rgyu yin te //
NG0201:293: na ga ra dza su ki ni s+t+wam shes de bzhin bskyed la //
NG0201:294: na ga ra dza ba su gi ni dza dza /
NG0201:296: de ltar gsal nas nyi shu pa nyid rtag par bzlas //
NG0201:297: ji ltar nus bzhin du mang bzlas te //
NG0201:298: de ltar bzlas tshe gzugs de ga bur gzhug / gzhan gyis mi mthong rang gi spyod yul nyid //
NG0201:299: rtags dang mtshan ma rang rang gzugs su 'byung *//
NG0201:300: bzlas pas skyo na mchod pa dbul par bya //
NG0201:301: na ga ra dza'i gzugs la thim par bsam //
NG0201:302: de nas gtad pa'i las byed 'dod na //
NG0201:303: bdag nyid mthu stobs bdag por bsam byas la //
NG0201:304: thugs kar mkha' lding ra dza gsal byas te //
NG0201:305: chu gtor mngar dang ldan pa sbyin byas la //
NG0201:306: seng ldeng phur pa bdag 'dra bsam //
NG0201:307: de yi gsang sngags nyid kyi byin gyis brlab //
NG0201:308: bdag gis de nyid dril zhing na gar bsdig / ka la ru pa tsag tshag dam dam //
NG0201:309: brgya'am stong du bzlas pa byas nas ni //
NG0201:310: gsang sngags 'di yis gtad par bya bar gsungs //
NG0201:311: a+om na ga ra dza dzahhum bam hoh /
NG0201:312: che ge mo a kar+sha ya a kar+sha ya hum /
NG0201:315: na ga chings na ga chings /
NG0201:316: na ga sdom na ga sdom /
NG0201:317: de skad ces ni lan gnyis brjod //
NG0201:318: mi 'di bdun rgyud rtsa ba chod //
NG0201:321: gdug pa klu yis dgra 'di ma bsad na //
NG0201:322: phyag na rdo rje rang gi mgo 'gems so //
NG0201:323: khong nas snying khrag 'dzag par byed //
NG0201:326: de nas gnan pa'i sngags 'di gsungs //
NG0201:327: mdze thod dam pha mes kyi thod pa ru //
NG0201:328: ming dang rus bcug sngo dmar skud pas bcings //
NG0201:329: bud med zhabs mas gtums la khyim gyi gting du sba //
NG0201:330: nub sgor kha bltas khyim gyi bdag po la //
NG0201:331: ba dmar glang dmar 'bri yi rwa co'i nang *//
NG0201:332: ming rus 'chi rkyen gang 'dod bris pa de //
NG0201:333: lto phye sbal lcong lto ru bcug nas ni //
NG0201:334: hum gis mtha' sgor ba ni tshig mi bya //
NG0201:335: kun la gang 'dod 'chi rkyen bris te sba /
NG0201:336: om lam sum lam pra ti sna nan ti ste ti sta /
NG0201:337: om che ge mo lam nan /
NG0201:340: om nam nam ti khas bye'u char khas /
NG0201:344: na ga pu ka na ga pu ka / na ga lam na ga lam swa ha /
NG0201:345: bdag la mi tshugs bya phyir gang mi smos //
NG0201:346: gnon pa'i rkang pa rdo rje rgya gram bsam //
NG0201:347: sa brko rang gi gri'am rab tu spang *//
NG0201:348: ma nyes dpang gzug lha srin dbang du bsdu //
NG0201:349: de ltar byas na las rnams nges par 'grub //
NG0201:350: dpal gshin rje zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:351: gdug pa klu nang ltar bsgrub pa'i skabs te nga drug pa'o ///
NG0201:352: / de nas klu'i drag sngags dgod pa'i sngags 'di gsungs /
NG0201:353: na ga ra dza ba su ki ni stam /
NG0201:354: na ga ra dza ba su ki ni dza dza /
NG0201:355: na ga ni na ga ni dza dza dza /
NG0201:356: yu yu yu dam pa ni /
NG0201:358: na ga ra dza ba su ki a mr-i ta sarba sa ma ya /
NG0201:359: na ga ra dza bi tso ka li /
NG0201:360: na ga ra dza rat+na na ga yu /
NG0201:361: na ga pu ka hum dza hum dza /
NG0201:362: om che ge mo dza dza dza /
NG0201:363: che ge mo sa ma ya dza dza /
NG0201:365: om na ga ra dza ba su ki dza dza /
NG0201:367: om na ga ra dza dzahhum bam hoh /
NG0201:368: che ge mo a' kar+sha ya a kar+sha ya hum tsin yang tsin yang */
NG0201:370: na ga chings na ga chings /
NG0201:373: na ga pu ka / na ga pu ka / hum dza hum dza /

NG0201:375: na ga ra dza ba su ki /
NG0201:376: dza dza dgra bo ma ra ya dza dza hum phat /

NG0201:379: om che ge mo lam nan /
NG0201:388: na ga pu ka / na ga pu ka / na ga lam /
NG0201:391: na ga ku+u ma ra b+h+yo nan /
NG0201:392: na ga ku ma ra b+h+yo //
NG0201:393: de bzhin sngags rnams rdzogs gyur na //
NG0201:394: mdze nad dz+wa la ma ra ya'o //
NG0201:395: 'jam dpal zla gsang nag po'i rgyud las /
NG0201:396: mdze nad dz+wa la klu'i zla gsang gi skabs te
NG0201:397: nga bdun pa'o // // de nas yang bcom ldan

NG0201:399: // rgyud kyi rgyal po zla gsang nag po 'di //

NG0201:402: 'khor khro bo dang khro mo dang */

NG0201:411: rgyud kyi rgyal po zla gsang nag po dang bcas

NG0201:414: phyogs skyong gshin rje yab yum dang */
NG0201:423: ma mo la sogs pa 'dus pa phal mo che
NG0201:424: rnams kyis shin tu ngam zhing ngo mtshar skyes nas
NG0201:425: bstod pa / e ma'o nyes bcom legs ldan mtshan bzhi mtha' las 'das //
NG0201:426: bdud dang gshin rje la sogs kun gyi gshed //
